<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 00:59:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>油价因对中国需求的担忧而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-tick-down-worries-about-chinese-demand-2024-07-16/</link><description>由于担心中国经济放缓抑制需求，油价周二小幅走低，不过越来越多的人认为美联储将在 9 月份开始降息，从而限制了跌幅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 00:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-tick-down-worries-about-chinese-demand-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国和英国需求疲软，Hugo Boss 下调全年销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-cuts-full-year-sales-guidance-over-weaker-demand-china-uk-2024-07-15/</link><description>由于全球消费者需求疲软，尤其是中国和英国等市场的消费者需求疲软，德国时装公司 Hugo Boss 周一将今年的销售指引下调至 42 亿欧元（45.8 亿美元）至 43.5 亿欧元之间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 22:30:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-cuts-full-year-sales-guidance-over-weaker-demand-china-uk-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国苦难加深，美国曲线陡峭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-15/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 21:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>包括哈马斯和法塔赫在内的巴勒斯坦派系将于七月在中国举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-factions-including-hamas-fatah-meet-china-july-2024-07-15/</link><description>两名哈马斯和法塔赫高级官员周一对路透表示，包括竞争对手哈马斯和法塔赫在内的巴勒斯坦派别将于 7 月在中国举行团结会谈，试图解决深刻的分歧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-factions-including-hamas-fatah-meet-china-july-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>审计证实世界游泳协会没有对中国兴奋剂案件处理不当</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/world-aquatics-did-not-mishandle-chinese-doping-cases-confirms-audit-2024-07-15/</link><description>世界游泳协会对中国游泳运动员药检呈阳性的处理情况进行的审计得出的结论是，管理机构没有管理不善或隐瞒情况，同时提出了恢复运动员对反兴奋剂系统信心的建议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:20:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/world-aquatics-did-not-mishandle-chinese-doping-cases-confirms-audit-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>德国经济部在欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的投票中投了弃权票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-economy-ministry-abstained-vote-eu-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-15/</link><description>德国经济部表示，在欧盟委员会周一讨论是否对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税时尚未做出决定，这实际上证实了其在周一投票中的弃权票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-economy-ministry-abstained-vote-eu-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，中国北方地区进入强降雨高度戒备状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-northern-region-high-alert-heavy-rainfall-xinhua-reports-2024-07-15/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社周一报道，中国当局已将北方地区置于暴雨高度戒备状态，并正在准备全面紧急措施以减轻影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-northern-region-high-alert-heavy-rainfall-xinhua-reports-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：国会称白宫应披露俄罗斯是否与中国分享美国武器见解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-should-disclose-whether-russia-sharing-us-weapons-insight-with-china-2024-07-15/</link><description>美国国会两党委员会周一敦促白宫披露俄罗斯是否与中国分享如何击败乌克兰战场上使用的美国武器的见解的细节。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/white-house-should-disclose-whether-russia-sharing-us-weapons-insight-with-china-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>淡马锡拟在印度投资100亿美元 应对中国压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/temasek-aims-invest-up-12-billion-india-china-weighs-2024-07-15/</link><description>新加坡国家投资者淡马锡一位高管周一表示，计划在三年内在印度金融服务和医疗保健等领域投资至多 100 亿美元，在印度对中国持谨慎态度之际，淡马锡对这个南亚国家有利。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:32:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/temasek-aims-invest-up-12-billion-india-china-weighs-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>该组织表示，欧洲需要独立于中国对关键矿产进行定价的方法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/europe-needs-way-price-critical-minerals-independently-china-group-says-2024-07-15/</link><description>一个欧盟资助组织的负责人表示，欧洲需要一个为能源转型所需的关键矿产定价的体系，该体系不依赖于中国，而中国在全球大部分行业中占据主导地位。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:08:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/europe-needs-way-price-critical-minerals-independently-china-group-says-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国海油报告渤海湾油气重大突破</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-reports-major-oil-gas-breakthrough-bohai-bay-2024-07-15/</link><description>中国国有石油天然气公司中海油周一表示，其在渤海湾实现勘探突破，经测试，可生产约210立方米原油和近100万立方米天然气。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-reports-major-oil-gas-breakthrough-bohai-bay-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>意大利、西班牙支持欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-spain-back-eu-tariffs-china-built-electric-vehicles-2024-07-15/</link><description>意大利和西班牙支持欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收关税，政府消息人士称，在周一午夜所有 27 个欧盟成员国就此事表明立场的最后期限之前。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:29:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-spain-back-eu-tariffs-china-built-electric-vehicles-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国顶级商品交易所降低对冲费用以提高参与度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shanghai-ine-dalian-exchange-halve-hedging-fees-2024-07-15/</link><description>中国两大主要商品交易所将把上市产品的套期保值费用减半，以降低用户成本并提高对全球最大商品消费国的参与度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:39:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shanghai-ine-dalian-exchange-halve-hedging-fees-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>业界称对关键矿产的投资存在疑问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/investment-critical-minerals-web-doubt-industry-says-2024-07-15/</link><description>业内人士表示，由于消费者对电动汽车的需求以及政府对零碳目标的承诺存在不确定性，许多公司不愿投资关键矿产和能源转型项目。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/investment-critical-minerals-web-doubt-industry-says-2024-07-15/</guid></item><item><title>解说：什么是中国的“三中全会”？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-is-chinas-third-plenum-2024-07-15/</link><description>中国执政的共产党周一召开了所谓的三中全会，这是一次大约每五年举行一次的重要会议，旨在制定国家长期社会和经济政策的总体方向。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 04:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-is-chinas-third-plenum-2024-07-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>